TopicTitle: Can someone please identify these parts?

Articles.Content:
Hey guys,

Recently I reinstalled KSP and forgot to backup my mods folder. There is a particular part I have been trying to find again without any luck. The part is an RCS thruster on a long extended arm.

I have an image of them below. Also if someone could tell me the parts that make up the satellite it would be awesome.
most of those look like kosmos parts in the center i cant tell what the strut ones are might me kosmos still.
I concur, everything to me looks like the Kosmos parts pack. It has with it the long arm RCS parts.
